{
  "stem": "13457.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that I ran inside, and I found there was a mob of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, always the danger of me being suffocated by the mob.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the kid as I was, I ran, and I hid myself on top of the big pile of, of sugar bags because they transporting in the hull of the ship sugar sa-- sacks of sugar.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got to Astrakhan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to Astrakhan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We started counting who, who made it to Astrakhan from that group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Turned out that some people couldn't make to the ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were either trapped or whatever, so we spent another couple of days, and they did come with the next ship.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we got on the trains, and we went deep inside Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to Altayskiy Kray.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The name of the place is Barnaul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The name of the place is Barnaul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As we were passing Novosibirsk, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got a fever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, there was-- there were lice on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You couldn't move your bowels because the trains were moving all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But then the question was what fever I got.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know how much it was, but it probably was like 105 or so fever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took me off the train in Barnaul and put me in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had violent diarrhea too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, turned out later that I had severe Streptococcal infection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother, I don't know in what way they got information that the hospital where my father was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] will be passing through Barnaul.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So both my sister and my mother were standing-- mind you this is Siberia.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
